[
    {
        "id": "act2_transition_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "好了好了，现在不是聊天的时候！",
        "next": "act2_transition_2"
    },
    {
        "id": "act2_transition_2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(突然变得严肃)",
        "next": "act2_transition_3"
    },
    {
        "id": "act2_transition_3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "我感应到了强烈的\"模因污染\"正在扩散，必须立刻建立防护圈境！",
        "next": "act2_transition_4"
    },
    {
        "id": "act2_transition_4",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(然后又有点紧张)",
        "next": "act2_transition_5"
    },
    {
        "id": "act2_transition_5",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "不过……这是我第一次在有人观看的情况下施展法典召唤……",
        "next": "act2_transition_6"
    },
    {
        "id": "act2_transition_6",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(小声嘀咕)",
        "next": "act2_transition_7"
    },
    {
        "id": "act2_transition_7",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "希望不要出什么差错……",
        "next": "codex_summoning_preparation_1"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_preparation_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(深吸一口气，摆出专业姿态)",
        "next": "codex_summoning_preparation_2"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_preparation_2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "现在，我将召唤\"万象法典\"。这是连接所有可能性的终极知识库。",
        "next": "codex_summoning_preparation_3"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_preparation_3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(突然想到什么，有点担心)",
        "next": "codex_summoning_preparation_4"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_preparation_4",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "但是……你确定要看吗？一旦接触法典，你就再也回不到普通的生活了。",
        "next": "codex_summoning_preparation_5"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_preparation_5",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(然后又小声补充)",
        "next": "codex_summoning_preparation_6"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_preparation_6",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "而且……万一我搞砸了，你可不能笑我……",
        "next": "male_encouragement_1"
    },
    {
        "id": "male_encouragement_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "陈星",
        "text": "我相信你。而且，我已经看到了这个世界的另一面，没有回头路了。",
        "next": "heroine_determination_1"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(被鼓励后，眼神变得坚定)",
        "next": "heroine_determination_2"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "好！那我就全力以赴了！",
        "next": "heroine_determination_3"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(开始认真地准备仪式)",
        "next": "heroine_determination_4"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_4",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "万象法典，听从我的召唤……",
        "next": "heroine_determination_5"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_5",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(突然停下)",
        "next": "heroine_determination_6"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_6",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "等等，我是不是应该先自我介绍一下？我叫魏娇娇，代号卡珊德拉，隶属于……",
        "next": "heroine_determination_7"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_7",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(意识到自己又跑题了)",
        "next": "heroine_determination_8"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_determination_8",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "啊！不对！现在是召唤时间！",
        "next": "codex_summoning_1"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(重新集中精神)",
        "next": "codex_summoning_2"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "万象法典，显现于此！",
        "next": "codex_summoning_3"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(符文开始在空中旋转)",
        "next": "codex_summoning_4"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_4",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "连接认知圈境，建立现实锚点！",
        "next": "codex_summoning_5"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_5",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
