    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_8",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "你看到了吗？这就是万象法典！",
        "next": "codex_summoning_9"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_9",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(然后又有点不好意思)",
        "next": "codex_summoning_10"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_summoning_10",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "虽然比预想的小了一点……",
        "next": "codex_explanation_1"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_explanation_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(指着法典)",
        "next": "codex_explanation_2"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_explanation_2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "这本法典记录了所有可能的故事线和现实分支。",
        "next": "codex_explanation_3"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_explanation_3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "每当有人创造新的故事，或者现实发生重大变化，法典都会自动更新。",
        "next": "codex_explanation_4"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_explanation_4",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(突然想到什么)",
        "next": "codex_explanation_5"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_explanation_5",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "对了！你想不想看看你自己的故事线？",
        "next": "codex_explanation_6"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_explanation_6",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "(兴奋地翻开法典)",
        "next": "codex_explanation_7"
    },
    {
        "id": "codex_explanation_7",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "让我找找……陈星……陈星……咦？怎么这么多页？",
        "next": "cognitive_realm_expansion_1"
    },
    {
        "id": "cognitive_realm_expansion_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "旁白",
        "text": "随着魏娇娇的吟唱，空间开始扭曲。",
        "next": "cognitive_realm_expansion_2"
    },
    {
        "id": "cognitive_realm_expansion_2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "旁白",
        "text": "现实的边界变得模糊，无数的可能性在眼前展开。",
