        "id": "heroine_realm_guide_3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "这里是万象行者的工作空间！左边是故事档案库，右边是现实修复工具箱……",
